source.name: ENERGY STAR Home Energy Yardstick
source.description: ENERGY STAR's Home Energy Yardstick allows homeowners to compare their energy use to others across the country to help decide if they should take action to improve the efficiency of their home. If you have five minutes and your last 12 months of utility bills, you are ready to use the Yardstick.
